  "text": "Overall, our data indicate that the syndecan family of HSPGs directly mediates binding, internalization, and lysosomal delivery of its ligands. Thus, syndecans act as receptors in vitro and might represent a physiologically important component of LDL receptor-independent catabolism of ligands in vivo [CITATION_1] .",
